metadata.name: Vitalik Clonkerin
metadata.description:
Our favourite dev, Vitalik Buterin, believes he created a monster with Ethereum. 

Back on Planet Clonk-9, infant Clonkies learn how to make their own cryptocurrency in roboschool, perhaps they should send their own Vitalik Clonkerin to help?


Dimensions: 2363 × 3150 pixels
Format: PNG
